Edwin Balmer and Philip Wylie

AFTER WORLDS COLLIDE

J. B. Lippincott Co., 1934. Hardcover. Fine / Very Good. Item #002322D

A fine, clean and tight hardcover copy in a very good, priced clipped jacket/brodart covered. 1933, 1934 dates on copyright page. Book is very nice. No bumped corners, no ownership signatures. Jacket is lightly soiled with small chips to all four corner folds. Small piece missing to bottom of jackets spine just under the L in Lippincott. A very decent copy. *** WE BOX AND SHIP ALL BOOKS WITH USPS TRACKING. *** WE HAVE BEEN BUYING AND SELLING USED BOOKS FOR OVER 37 YEARS.
